data.title: Course Catalog
data.meta_description: See the full catalog for upcoming courses, lectures and events from FIU's Osher Lifelong Learning Institute.
data.text:
Please note that as a small, but nimble and dynamic OLLI, we are always working on new program ideas and are adding new classes, courses, and seminars to our Course Catalog on a regular basis. Make sure to check back in with us often so that you will not miss a particular class or event!

View Our OLLI at FIU CODE OF CONDUCT
